                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in black ink. The first letter in a new pargraph consists of a captal placed in a separate column in the outer margin, e.g. <locus from="3r" to="3r" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>
